    "description": "Genetec Corporation engages in the contract development of software and hardware related to embedded systems in Japan. It operates through three segments: System Solutions Business, Engineering Solutions Business, and GPS Business. The company is involved in software development for embedded systems, web applications, servers, and cloud computing, as well as system development, development category, cybersecurity consulting, FPGA/board design and development, and IoT/M2M business; and offers CAD/CAM systems, 3D simulation, offline teaching, operation monitoring, PLM, ALM, and SAP consulting. It also provides COCODAYO, a location information sharing application for disasters and emergencies; and GPS solutions for corporations and local governments. The company was incorporated in 1985 and is headquartered in Shinjuku, Japan."
